Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:39.03,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}未來一定就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:44.58,Asteroid - OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}所以邁開步伐啟程吧
